  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A two-step multi-centre study with 240 rheumatoid arthritis patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A two-step multi-centre study containing:

      A test-retest study including 180 patients filling in questionnaires and performing joint
      assessments to assess reliability of patient generated data

      AND

      An agreement study focusing on questionnaires and joint assessments performed by 60 patients,
      a medical student, a physician and by an ultrasound-examinator assessing agreement between
      the four assessors
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
